pytest-stub changelog
=====================


v1.1.0 [2020-04-28]
-------------------
+ Added '[mock_persist]' shortcut support.
+ Added 'stub_global()' for global stubbing.


v1.0.0 [2020-04-18]
-------------------
! Dropped QA for Python 3.4.
+ Added '[mock]' shortcut support.
+ Now can stub entire modules (e.g. 'x' for 'import x').


v0.1.0
------
+ Basic functionality.